<br>
<br>
Check out my magelo and see my gimp gear.  Some of it is very nice, I can actually quad in PoV now so I've gotten to my first goal.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=400296" target="top">Kacaroto's Magelo</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
When I leave VT I want to be at FT15, all resists at or above 200 unbuffed.  I know of a few items I'd want like the Leggings of Secrets for the focus, and the Ring of Flamewarding.<br>
<br>
So yall give me some good ideas for what to look for when I raid there.<br>
<br>
Kacaroto<br>
<br>
btw, my guild also does Seru/Emp <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ghode>Ghode</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 336<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/28/03 1:41 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Time for upgrades in VT...</span><hr size=1> Being in a roatation it will be hard to get all those stats fast. Here are some items to look out for though.<br>
<br>
Living Symbol from the TVKs<br>
Cap of the Silent star from the TVKs<br>
Shade stone amulet from Blob1<br>
Amulet of Xuzl from DXV<br>
Grimoire of Enhancement from DXV<br>
Ring of flame warding from DXXT<br>
Robe of Luring Shawdows from DXXT<br>
Belt of dark Thought from DXXT<br>
FT4 cloak from TVK<br>
Lightbringers Earring from DXVT<br>
Caster arms from DXVT<br>
Twilight shroud (if your not planning on getting an emp robe)<br>
Necklace of Endless Concepts from Mini Aten<br>
Crown of Energy from the two 2 blobs<br>
Shield of Energy from the 2 blobs<br>
and of course the Caster loots(secrets) from Aten. I'd hold out for Mask/Legs, they seem to have the most useful focus effects.<br>
Soul essense of Aten from AHR<br>
<br>
There is a lot more, but these are  what comes to mind atm. I use <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.darkwind-guild.com/SoL/Luclin/VT.htm">www.darkwind-guild.com/SoL/Luclin/VT.htm</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> when i want to look at VT item stats and their focus effects.<br>
<br>
