<br>
In my opinion, some of the better investments from VT include:<br>
- Umbricite Hoop<br>
- Ring of Flamewarding<br>
- Ring of Immobilization<br>
- Lightbringer Earring<br>
- Sanguine Robe (mmm hitpoints and regen!)<br>
- Shade Stone Amulet<br>
- Mask of Secrets (higher mana preservation than preservation of xegony, I believe)<br>
- Shield of Energy (mmm flowing thought!)<br>
<br>
I use darkwind guild's listing to look up stats on pieces from VT, I forget the URL offhand... But these are some nicer pieces that'll last for a long time.  Hope this helps a bit. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.rpi.edu/~hammos/eq/kourinsig.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=48970">Sage Kourin Nee`lahn</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> -- <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://leviathan.two-monkeys.com">Leviathan</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> -- Stormhammer</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ajilon>Ajilon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>KAfekinBOOM!</span><br>  Posts: 857<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/17/03 2:15 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re: try this?</span><hr size=1> Armguard of Purity is pretty nice and you can hold onto it for quite awhile.  Effect would be useful if they would move it to 5 sec cast time though.<br>
<br>
Twilight shroud if you dont get Emp robe, as already mentioned.  It's a great shoulder item but it's effect doesnt stack with Koadics robe.<br>
<br>
Mask of Secrets is really nice, wish I had that instead of Tome.<br>
<br>
Robe of Secrets is ok, I like having the stats and saves, it's FT7 but effect Evo +10% is about worthless.  Good robe to have if you miss out on Emp Robe.<br>
<br>
Sceptre of Calekor, I like this one because it's pretty versatile going in range, primary and secondary and has decent stats/saves.  The BoR focus effect is complete garbage though because it's not broken, players are just already innate above BoR's bonus once they hit L65.  So thats a bullshit effect which should be tuned.  Another nice bit about this one is in my guild the Sceptre was very cheap on loot points cost.<br>
<br>
Let (encourage!) the other guild wizards get the staff that does SS manafree unless you want to be spellshield bitch during PoP mobs <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Cord of Insight,  kinda nice because it can be worn in either bracer or belt slot.<br>
